## Description {#details}

An abstract base class for various kinds of location tables (.debug&#95;loc, .debug&#95;loclists, and their dwo variants).

## Public Member Functions

### dumpLocationList() {#aec9a11e9a2e87414bb67f6aaa342a570}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>bool DWARFLocationTable::dumpLocationList (uint64&#95;t &#42; Offset, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/raw-ostream">raw&#95;ostream</a> &amp; OS, std::optional&lt; <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/object/sectionedaddress">object::SectionedAddress</a> &gt; BaseAddr, <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfobject">DWARFObject</a> &amp; Obj, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfunit">DWARFUnit</a> &#42; U, <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/didumpoptions">DIDumpOptions</a> DumpOpts, unsigned Indent) const</>}>
Dump the location list at the given <code>Offset</code>.

The function returns true iff it has successfully reched the end of the list. This means that one can attempt to parse another list after the current one (<code>Offset</code> will be updated to point past the end of the current list).

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-h/#l00067">67</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-h">DWARFDebugLoc.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-cpp/#l00122">122</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-cpp">DWARFDebugLoc.cpp</a>.

### visitLocationList() {#ab23c0a6b21464e995ec595578c63ffcb}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>virtual Error llvm::DWARFLocationTable::visitLocationList (uint64&#95;t &#42; Offset, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/function-ref">function&#95;ref</a>&lt; bool(<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/dwarflocationentry">DWARFLocationEntry</a> &amp;)&gt; Callback) const</>}>
Call the user-provided callback for each entry (including the end-of-list entry) in the location list starting at <code>Offset</code>.

The callback can return false to terminate the iteration early. Returns an error if it was unable to parse the entire location list correctly. Upon successful termination <code>Offset</code> will be updated point past the end of the list.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-h/#l00059">59</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugloc-h">DWARFDebugLoc.h</a>.
